These pages are the book's back-matter **index**, covering entries
from "Patti, Adelina" through "Tahiti." No narrative content appears
here — only alphabetical reference entries. Notes below capture the
thematic structure visible in the index itself, which reveals the
book's key subjects and the density of coverage for each.

